    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，双向合并是指develop往main合并，同时main也要同步回develop对吧？那第一次develop切出来后，需要先提交一个commit再开始合并吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
