    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，develop上至少要有实际提交才能演示合并。流程是：develop提交后，切回main把develop合并进来；然后再切到develop，把更新后的main合并回去；最后develop再提交一次，main再合并develop。这样形成双向同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "checkout",
        "merge",
        "commit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我来构建这个结构。先初始化main分支做第一个commit，然后checkout到develop分支并添加提交。接着切回main执行第一次merge develop。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，main合并develop之后，记得还要给main再加一个commit，模拟发布后的热修复或者版本标记，然后再往develop同步。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit",
        "develop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，所以main在第一次merge之后要有一个commit，然后checkout develop把main合并进去，develop再提交一次，最后main再合并develop完成双向闭环。标题定为\"Two-way merges (CloudNative_Serverless)\"可以吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "develop",
        "commit",
        "checkout",
        "merge",
        "title"
